{
  "stem": "1132.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you got any food, you paid a very high price for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it usually came through the superintendent of the building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's the recollection that I do have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have recollections of my sister and my mother [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] being the people, obviously, to whom I was looking up to.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And wondering as to what was going to happen, and waiting my clue and my cue as to what was happening from them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have memories of having a favorite doll, and that doll came with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the only toy that came with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if you recall, I said we left in the middle of the night our original apartment building, and then we went into hiding in this building.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that doll went through as much with me as I went through basically.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was the only toy that I remember having.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember people not really doing anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have no recollection in this setup of people playing cards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "For example, as previously I mentioned, we were playing cards to kill time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I have absolutely no recollection of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I have clear recollection of the people in the-- in this room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody on everybody else's nerve.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody on everybody else's back literally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What-- how what we knew what went on, we only knew as to what went on the outside if the super came in or if somebody like my father came in who was carefully watching as to what was going on.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we knew that things were getting tougher and tougher, and the fighting was getting closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's the recollection and that's the memory that I do have.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
